title: Episode 164: Austen Summers - Do You Even Game?
description:
Show Notes:

In this episode I interview Austen Summers, an awesome dude who really walks the walk of a dating strategist and expert.

We go into great detail on how to get over anxiety, how often you should be approaching, how to use voice notes and how to optimize your Instagram.

You can tell by Austen's presence and attitude that he's the type of guy that women adore and a great coach and mentor that like minded guys can model on their journey.

https://www.instagram.com/austensummers/
